```python
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

df_meas = pd.DataFrame({
    "run": ["R1"]*6 + ["R2"]*6,
    "day": [1,2,3,4,5,6]*2,
    "ph":  [7.1, 7.05, 6.95, 6.9, 6.85, 6.8,
            7.2, 7.15, 7.1, 7.05, 7.0, 6.95],
    "titer": [1.8, 2.0, 2.3, 2.6, 2.8, 3.0,
              1.5, 1.7, 1.9, 2.1, 2.2, 2.3]
})
df_spec = pd.DataFrame({
    "run": ["R1","R1","R2"],
    "start_day": [1, 4, 2],
    "end_day":   [3, 6, 6],
    "ph_low":    [6.9, 6.8, 7.0]
})
display(df_meas, df_spec)
```

# ÌíÄÏù¥

```python
tmp = pd.merge(df_meas, df_spec, how='left', on='run')
df_merged = tmp[(tmp['day']>=tmp['start_day']) & (tmp['day']<=tmp['end_day'])].reset_index(drop=True)
display(df_merged)
df_merged['out_of_spec']= df_merged['ph'] <df_merged['ph_low']
display(df_merged)
df_merged_sorted=df_merged.sort_values(by=['run', 'day'], ascending=[True,True])
run_feat = df_merged_sorted.groupby('run').agg(
    oos_cnt = ('out_of_spec', 'sum'),
    oos_rate = ('out_of_spec', 'mean'),
    titer_last = ('titer', 'last')
).reset_index()
display(run_feat)
run_feat['grade'] = np.where(run_feat['oos_rate']>=0.4,'RED', np.where(run_feat['oos_rate']>=0.2, 'YELLOW', 'GREEN'))
display(run_feat)
```

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
fig, axes = plt.subplots(ncols=1, nrows=2, figsize=(7,6))
runs = ['R1', 'R2']
for idx, run in enumerate(runs):
    x = df_merged[df_merged['run']==run]['day']
    y = df_merged[df_merged['run']==run]['ph']
    scatter_x = df_merged[(df_merged['run']==run)&(df_merged['out_of_spec'])]['day']
    scatter_y = df_merged[(df_merged['run']==run)&(df_merged['out_of_spec'])]['ph']
    ph_low = df_merged[(df_merged['run']==run)]['ph_low'][0]
    axes[idx].plot(x,y)
    axes[idx].scatter(scatter_x,scatter_y, color='red')
    axes[idx].axhline(ph_low, color='gray', linestyle='--')
    axes[idx].grid(False)
plt.show()
```
